This is a '''list of bantamweight boxing champions''', as recognized by [[boxing]] organizations:
* The [[World Boxing Association]] (WBA), established in 1921 as the National Boxing Association (NBA). * The [[World Boxing Council]] (WBC), established in 1963. * The [[International Boxing Federation]] (IBF), established in 1983. * The [[World Boxing Organization]] (WBO), established in 1988.
